#. (itstool) path: section/para
#: C/index.docbook:355
msgid ""
"You can select which audio file format <application>Sound Juicer</"
"application> uses to store your tracks on your computer. There are a number "
"of available formats, each with its own advantages. The available formats "
"on your computer may vary, but the following choices are usually available:"
msgstr ""
"Компьютеріңізде тректерді сақтау үшін <application>Sound Juicer</"
